trait-name-Shadowkin = Shadowkin
trait-description-Shadowkin =
    Your mind has touched the darkness.
    A painful interaction with the bluespace dimension has made you an heir to the powers of an extinct race.

    - You can only learn "Shadeskip" and "DarkSwap".
    - Other psionic disciplines are no longer accessible to you.

trait-name-Infernal = Infernal
trait-description-Infernal =
    The discovery of anomaly research technology led to the emergence of "Infernals".
    These psionics draw their powers from the dimension of infinite fiery Gehenna,
    Making them extremely dangerous beings that Epistemics would like to... take under control.

    - All your abilities belong exclusively to the "Pyrokinesis" class.
    - Other psionic disciplines are no longer accessible to you.

trait-name-Telekineticist = Telekineticist
trait-description-Telekineticist =
    Telekineticists are one of the oldest branches of psychics, known even in ancient treatises as "Scribes of Pure Will."
    Telekineticist manipulate the fundamental forces of pressure, inertia, and vector.
    Their abilities range from chaotic waves of energy to precise manipulations of space.

    - All your abilities belong exclusively to the "Kinesis" class.
    - Other psionic disciplines are no longer accessible to you.

trait-name-Priest = Priest
trait-description-Priest =
    "Priests" are a phenomenon that humanity observed long before it learned to explain psionics.
    Shamans, healers, priests — all of them were the first Priests who touched the birth of the universe.
    One day, the lesser secret of life was revealed to you. Will you be able to comprehend more?

    - All your abilities belong exclusively to the "Life" class.
    - Other psionic disciplines are no longer accessible to you.

